                                <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread"><aura:if isTrue="{! !v.form.isCRC}">Q3. Time commitment</aura:if><aura:if isTrue="{! v.form.isCRC}">Q2. Time commitment</aura:if></div>
                                <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread"><i>Each investigator should state time commitment towards following activities.</i></div>
