                        </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                            <br/>
                            <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">Q1. Since the research will be conducted at multiple locations, please provide details of fund sharing. In case of award, India Alliance would only send funds to Sponsoring institution of the PI. The funds would be given in INR.</div><br/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                            <table class="slds-table slds-table_cell-buffer slds-table_bordered">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr class="slds-line-height_reset">
                                        <th class="" scope="col">
                                            <div class=" " title="Location">Location</div>
                                        </th>
                                        <th class="" scope="col">
                                            <div class=" " title="Total Funds requested (INR)">Total Funds requested (INR)</div>
                                        </th>
                                        <th class="" scope="col">
                                            <div class=" " title="Percentage of total funds ">Percentage of total funds </div>
                                        </th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <aura:iteration var="investigator" items="{!v.form.investigatorRecordList}" indexVar="indx">
