                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="">
                                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                                        <lightning:input type="number" label="" value="{!investigator.investigatorRecord.Total_Funds_requested_INR__c}" formatter="currency" step="0.01" onchange="{!c.calculateFundPercentage}"/>
                                                    </aura:if>
                                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                                        {!investigator.investigatorRecord.Total_Funds_requested_INR__c}
                                                    </aura:if>
                                                </div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="">
                                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                                        <lightning:input type="number" label="" value="{!investigator.investigatorRecord.Percentage_of_total_funds__c}"  step="0.01" disabled="true"/>
                                                    </aura:if>
                                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                                        {!investigator.investigatorRecord.Percentage_of_total_funds__c}
                                                    </aura:if>
                                                </div>
                                            </th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </aura:iteration>
                                </tbody>
                            </table><br/>
                            <div class="">While working on the budget please be mindful of our <a href="https://www.indiaalliance.org/costing-policies-grants" target="_blank">grant costing policies</a>, particularly the disallowed costs. All requests made in this section should be commensurate with the objectives of the proposal and supported with strong justification.</div>
                            <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread">The total costs must be within the amount requested (Z). This includes the direct cost requested on the application (A) and institutional overheads (B).</div><br/>
                            
                            <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12" style="text-align: center;">
                                <br/>
                                <table class="slds-table slds-table_cell-buffer slds-table_bordered">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr class="slds-line-height_reset">
                                            <th class="" scope="col" colspan="3">
                                                <div class=" " title="Budget overview" style="text-align:center;">Budget overview</div>
                                            </th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr class="slds-line-height_reset">
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="1.">1.</div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="Salaries for PIs*">Salaries for PIs*</div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="{!v.form.totalYearAmount }"><ui:outputCurrency value="{!v.form.totalYearAmount }"/> </div>
                                            </th>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="slds-line-height_reset">
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="2.">2.</div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="Support Staff salaries ">Support Staff salaries </div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="{!v.form.budget.totalsfAmount }"><ui:outputCurrency value="{!v.form.budget.totalsfAmount }"/></div>
                                            </th>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr class="slds-line-height_reset"> 
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="3.">3.</div>
                                            </th>
                                            <th class="" scope="col">
                                                <div class=" " title="Materials and consumables ">Materials and consumables </div>
                                            </th>
