                            <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread">This can cover cost for PIs and support staff employed on the grant to (i) attend research meetings/conferences/symposiums; (ii) collaborative visits; and (iii) fieldwork and sample collection.</div>
