                            <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">10. India Alliance contributions
                                <br/>Flexible Funding Allowance: The India Alliance recognizes that unanticipated costs might arise during the tenure of the project. Therefore, in addition to the requested costs, the India Alliance will provide fixed contingency funds called Flexible Funding Allowance.<br/></div>
