                                <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">Q1. Does your proposal include working with human participants, experiments with human stem cells, biological samples and/or personal data relating to living or dead persons? <br/>If yes, please tick as appropriate: </div><br/>
