                                    <br/><br/>
                                    <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">Q2. Please state: By whom and when the ethics of the project was/will be reviewed? Also specify any other regulatory approvals that have been/will be obtained. (Limit 200 words)</div>
