                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/><br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q3. If your project involves Experiments with human stem cells, respond to the following questions: <br/>Does the institution where the work is to be carried out have approval from India’s National Apex Committee for Stem Cell Research and Therapy (<a href="http://bic.icmr.org.in/nacscrt/" target="_blank">NAC-SCRT</a>)?</div>
