                                    <div class="">Based on the source(s) of stem cells and nature of experiments, the list of restricted areas of research is available at <a href="http://bic.icmr.org.in/nacscrt/index.html" target="_blank">ICMR website</a>. The NAC-SCRT is authorized to review approve and monitor the type of studies listed under prohibited areas of research as outlined in the ICMR guidelines through IC-SCR/IEC.</div>
                                </div>
