                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">•	PIs must refer to the <a href="https://www.indiaalliance.org/award-policies" target="_blank">India Alliance’s policy on the use of animals in biomedical research</a>. For further information regarding the National Centre for the Replacement, Refinement and Reduction of Animals in Research (NC3Rs), please see <a href="https://www.nc3rs.org.uk/" target="_blank">www.nc3rs.org.uk</a>.</div>
                                    <div class="">•	All applications involving the use of primates, cats, dogs and Equidae animals, or their tissue/data will be further reviewed by the NC3Rs.The office may approach you with additional questions in this regard. </div>
                                    <div class="">•	All proposed research involving genetically altered mice are expected to consider the welfare assessment set up on <a href="https://www.nc3rs.org.uk/generation-and-breeding-genetically-altered-mice" target="_blank">NC3Rs website</a>. </div>
                                    <div class="">•	The institution where the animal work is to be carried out must have approval from CPCSEA or SCLA. This should be confirmed in your application.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q2. Please provide details of any procedures on animals of substantial or moderate severity? (Limit 200 words)</div>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                        <lightning:textarea class="200" onchange="{!c.validateTextArea}" name="" label="" value="{!v.form.grantRecord.Details_Procedures_of_Animals__c}"/>    
                                    </aura:if>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                        {!v.form.grantRecord.Details_Procedures_of_Animals__c}
                                    </aura:if>
                                    
                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q3. Why is animal use necessary? Are there other possible approaches? (Limit 200 words)</div>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                        <lightning:textarea class="200" onchange="{!c.validateTextArea}" name="" label="" value="{!v.form.grantRecord.Why_is_animal_use_necessary__c}"/>    
                                    </aura:if>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                        {!v.form.grantRecord.Why_is_animal_use_necessary__c}
                                    </aura:if>
                                    
                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q4. If you plan to work on animal stem cells, please provide details of source of stem cells and nature of experiments. The institution where the work is to be carried out should have the IC-SCR or IAEC with required expertise to review the stem cell research in place. Please confirm this in your response to this question. </div>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                        <lightning:textarea maxlength="" name="" label="" value="{!v.form.grantRecord.plan_to_work_on_animal_stem_cells__c}"/>    
                                    </aura:if>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                        {!v.form.grantRecord.plan_to_work_on_animal_stem_cells__c}
                                    </aura:if>
                                    
                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q5. Indicate if any of the following species will be used: <br/>Primate, Cat, Dog, Equidae, Pig, Genetically Altered Animals? If yes, the office may contact you with additional questions. </div>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
                                        <lightning:textarea maxlength="" name="" label="" value="{!v.form.grantRecord.following_species_will_be_used__c}"/>    
                                    </aura:if>
                                    <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
                                        {!v.form.grantRecord.following_species_will_be_used__c}
                                    </aura:if>
                                    
                                </div>
                                <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                    <br/>
                                    <div class="QuestionClass">Q6. Why are the species to be used the most appropriate? (Limit 250 words)</div>
