                            </div>
                            <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                <br/><br/>
                                <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">Q1. Please confirm that you have considered whether your proposed research or its outcomes pose risk of being misused for harmful purposes. If you have identified potential “non-hypothetical” risks, please describe briefly the steps that you and your institution will take to manage them (Limit 250 words).</div><br/>
                                <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}">
