                                </aura:if>
                                
                            </div>
                            <div class="slds-col slds-size_1-of-1 slds-large-size_12-of-12">
                                <br/><br/>
                                <div class="QuestionClass">Q2. If applicable, let us know details of </div><br/>
                                <div class="">(i) Technology, materials, or other inventions that you may use for this project that are subject to any patents or other form of intellectual property protection, if any.</div>
                                <div class="">Agreements with commercial, academic, or other organisations, including arrangements with collaborators named in the grant application that might lead to intellectual property issues or restrictions. India Alliance policies and award conditions are indicated at <a href="https://www.indiaalliance.org/award-conditions" target="_blank">https://indiaalliance.org/award-conditions</a> and <a href="https://indiaalliance.org/award-policies" target="_blank">https://indiaalliance.org/award-policies</a> (Limit 200 words) </div>
                                <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode=='read'}">
