                                <br/><br/>
                                <div class="slds-progress__item_content slds-grid slds-grid_align-spread QuestionClass">You may suggest up to 3 potential reviewers who may be appropriate to evaluate your proposal. Likewise, let us know if we should not approach someone to review your application (up to 3). Both the lists should be reasonable and supported with a justification.  </div><br/>
                                <br/>
                                <aura:if isTrue="{!v.defaultMode!='read'}"><div style="text-align:right;"><lightning:button variant="" label="Add Reviewer and Restriction" value="{! v.form.grantRecord.Id}" name="v.showAddRAR" class="grantIdrar"  title="Add Reviewer and Restriction" onclick="{! c.openModal }" /></div></aura:if>
                                <div class="tableScroll">
                                    <table class="slds-table slds-table_cell-buffer slds-table_bordered">
                                        <thead>
