                                    <div class="">The undertaking from the sponsor(s) at the host institution(s) should be issued in the format given below. It should be issued on institutional letterhead with date, full name of the person who is signing the undertaking along with his/her designation. This undertaking should be provided by sponsors of all Investigators. All the undertakings should be attached with the application at the time of submission. <br/>In case of an award, the funds will be transferred to the Sponsoring institution of the Principal Investigator. All the participating institutions would be required to sign a contract/agreement for fund disbursement before activation of the award. </div>
